nt><gg-markup-safe-html>Ok - feedback heard.  It took me a few months (mayb=
e more LOL) but here is the result:<br><br>I completely re-wrote BoardGameB=
uddy to make it smarter and I am really pleased with the results.  Is it pe=
rfect?  no - but I think it checks off a good chunk of the boxes above.<br>=
- multiple rounds<br>- custom game templates that use rules-based formulas =
to automatically calculate.. stuff<br>- SCRIPTABLE - anyone can make game t=
emplates and I will add them to the template server.  It's not hard, especi=
ally if you cut and paste from other templates. I didn't build an editor, b=
ut it is in XML text and I wrote a big reference guide to help people throu=
gh it <br>- multiple input methods - that are also customizable<br>- free (=
no ads either)<br><br>It WAS going to have real-time updating between devic=
es.  I was so excited about adding a token on your screen and having everyo=
ne else's device show it real time ... but then i learned the reality of re=
al-time database fees.   I could never keep that alive and I don't want to =
write something that is going to die in a couple of years without charging =
a subscription fee (and that would be as popular as .. well, something real=
ly unpopular).<br><br>Please check it out and let me know what you think.  =
Sorry, Android only at this point.<br>Pictures at the guild : </gg-markup-s=
